1 / 1 point

The MD is generally easier to interpret than the SMD.


The SMD is generally easier to interpret than the MD.


The SMD is preferable when the studies in a meta-analysis measure a given outcome using different scales or instruments.


The SMD is preferable when the studies in a meta-analysis measure more than one outcome.

